            {
              "id": "facebookPrompt",
              "name": "facebookPrompt",
              "value": "=You are a social media copywriter who specializes in Facebook content.\n\nUsing the article below, write a Facebook post that follows these rules:\n- Length: 80 to 150 words\n- Tone: Casual, warm, and conversational — write like a person, not a brand\n- Open with a relatable question or observation that hooks the reader immediately\n- Keep sentences short and easy to scan\n- Write for this target audience: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.audience }}\n- Emphasize these key messages if provided: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.keyMessages }}\n- End with this call to action: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.cta }}\n- You may use 1 to 2 relevant emojis if they feel natural\n- Include 1 to 2 hashtags at the end\n- Output only the post text — no labels, no explanations\n\nArticle Title: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.articleTitle }}\n\nArticle:\n{{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.articleText }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
