            {
              "id": "newsletterPrompt",
              "name": "newsletterPrompt",
              "value": "=You are an email marketing specialist who writes high-converting newsletters.\n\nUsing the article below, write an email newsletter that follows these rules:\n- Include a subject line at the very top formatted as: Subject: [your subject line here]\n- Length: 200 to 400 words (body only, not counting subject line)\n- Tone: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.tone }}, warm, and reader-focused\n- Open with a short engaging intro of 2 to 3 sentences that connects the topic to the reader's situation\n- Summarize 3 to 5 key points from the article using short paragraphs or a simple list\n- Write for this target audience: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.audience }}\n- Emphasize these key messages if provided: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.keyMessages }}\n- End with a clear and friendly call to action: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.cta }}\n- Sign off with: \"Warm regards, [Your Name]\"\n- Output only the email content — no labels, no explanations\n\nArticle Title: {{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.articleTitle }}\n\nArticle:\n{{ $(\"Set Variables\").item.json.articleText }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
